---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Downstage FAQ | What it is and how to get started
description: Common questions about Downstage — what it is, why to use it over a word processor, how to start, and how it compares to other tools.
bodyClass: docs-page
permalink: /faq/
---
<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-6 px-4 py-4 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[280px_minmax(0,1fr)] lg:px-8">
  <button
    type="button"
    class="mobile-menu-toggle fixed right-4 top-4 z-50 inline-flex min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px] items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-[rgba(35,22,20,0.92)] text-parchment-200 shadow-stage backdrop-blur-xl lg:hidden"
    data-mobile-menu-toggle
    data-mobile-menu-target="faq-mobile-menu"
    data-mobile-menu-backdrop="faq-mobile-menu-backdrop"
    aria-expanded="false"
    aria-controls="faq-mobile-menu"
    aria-label="Open FAQ menu"
  >
    <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="2">
      <path d="M4 7h16"></path>
      <path d="M4 12h16"></path>
      <path d="M4 17h16"></path>
    </svg>
    <span class="sr-only">Open FAQ menu</span>
  </button>
  <div
    id="faq-mobile-menu-backdrop"
    class="mobile-menu-backdrop hidden lg:hidden"
    data-mobile-menu-backdrop-panel="faq-mobile-menu"
  ></div>
  <div
    id="faq-mobile-menu"
    class="mobile-menu-panel hidden lg:hidden"
    data-mobile-menu-panel
    aria-label="FAQ menu"
  >
    <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 no-underline" href="{{ '/' | url }}">
      <img class="h-12 w-12 object-contain" src="{{ '/downstage_logo.png' | url }}" alt="Downstage logo">
      <span class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-parchment-200">Downstage</span>
    </a>
    <p class="mb-5 mt-3 leading-7 text-parchment-300">What Downstage is, why to use it, and how to get started.</p>
    <nav aria-label="Section navigation" class="docs-nav-sections js-section-nav grid gap-1">
      {% for section in collections.faqSections %}
        <a class="nav-link rounded-xl px-3 py-2 text-sm text-parchment-300 transition hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-parchment-200" href="#{{ section.data.id }}">{{ section.data.navTitle or section.data.title }}</a>
      {% endfor %}
    </nav>
    <div class="mt-5 border-t border-white/10 pt-4">
      <p class="px-3 pb-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-brass-300">Project resources</p>
      <div class="grid gap-1">
        <a class="nav-link rounded-xl px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-brass-300 transition hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-brass-300" href="{{ '/start/' | url }}">Start Here</a>
        <a class="nav-link rounded-xl px-3 py-2 text-sm text-parchment-300 transition hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-parchment-200" href="{{ '/editor/' | url }}">Web Editor</a>
        <a class="nav-link rounded-xl px-3 py-2 text-sm text-parchment-300 transition hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-parchment-200" href="{{ '/syntax/' | url }}">Syntax Guide</a>
        <a class="nav-link rounded-xl px-3 py-2 text-sm text-parchment-300 transition hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-parchment-200" href="{{ '/' | url }}">Home</a>
        <a class="nav-link rounded-xl px-3 py-2 text-sm text-parchment-300 transition hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-parchment-200" href="https://github.com/jscaltreto/downstage#readme">Project README</a>
        <a class="nav-link rounded-xl px-3 py-2 text-sm text-parchment-300 transition hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-parchment-200" href="https://github.com/jscaltreto/downstage/blob/main/SPEC.md">Full Specification</a>
        <a class="nav-link rounded-xl px-3 py-2 text-sm text-parchment-300 transition hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-parchment-200" href="https://github.com/jscaltreto/downstage">Source on GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
